Shenzhen Tianma Microelectronics Co Ltd

- China
					
					(Guangdong)
				
				


















































Tianma Microelectronics Co., Ltd. is specializing in producing Liquid Crystal Display (LCD) and Liquid Crystal Module (LCM). The company has three LCD plants and two LCM plants, with an annual capacity of 200,000 square meters of LCD and 50 million pieces of LCM. 

Tianma offers one-package service, including consulting, design, production and sale of LCD and LCM, with professional technical support. The main products include TN, STN, CSTN LCD panel and SMT, COB, TAB COG, COF and TFT or OLED module products.
Tianma Microelectronics Co., Ltd. is specializing in producing Liquid Crystal Display (LCD) and Liquid Crystal Module (LCM). The company has three LCD plants and two LCM plants, with an annual capacity of 200,000 square meters of LCD and 50 million pieces of LCM. 

Tianma offers one-package service, including consulting, design, production and sale of LCD and LCM, with professional technical support. The main products include TN, STN, CSTN LCD panel and SMT, COB, TAB COG, COF and TFT or OLED module products.Less





















