                                    About Tianma


 Location：Home > About Us > About Tianma




Tianma Microelectronics Co., Ltd. (Tianma) specializes in providing display solutions and efficient support services worldwide. We were originally established in 1983 and publicly listed on t Shenzhen Stock Exchange (SZ. 000050) in 1995.  
















	   Our company is committed to providing leading technology and quality products to the consumer and professional display industries that are used in applications to include smart phones, tablet PCs, smart wear, automotive instrumentation, industrial and medical instrumentation, avionic display, home automation, etc.


	 


	    Tianma’s shipments of small and medium size modules kept the leading position among the global panel factories. Our market share for high-end medical devices, aviation entertainment, navigation and VOIP products ranked first worldwide. Many customers have chosen to release their new products globally equipped with Tianma display products and our products are also ranked first in quality for many of customers. Tianma is committed to continuous innovation, better customer service and supports different requirements for applications in the field.
    


	    Tianma has clear technological and production advantages in the small and medium size display market where it has enjoyed a strong market presence over the years. Tianma has established a National R&D Laboratory on TFT-LCD Key Materials and Technologies, a National Enterprise Technology Center, and a post-doctoral workstation to enhance the knowledge and technical expertise of our employees. We also undertake multiple major national projects from the National Development and Reform Commission, Ministry of Science and Technology, and Ministry of Industry.


	 


	    The possession of new technologies including LTPS-TFT, Oxide-TFT, AMOLED displays, Flexible displays, Transparent displays, 3D displays and In-cell/On-cell integrated touch technology set the foundation for innovation and the development of new and exciting products.


	 


	    We have a comprehensive production line combination including G4.5/G5 a-Si TFT–LCD, G5.5 LTPS TFT-LCD, plus one G5.5 AMOLED line and two new G6 LTPS TFT-LCD lines under construction, enabling Tianma to achieve the highest possible level of product quality and supply capability. Tianma was the first to start mass production from a G5.5 LTPS production line in China. In addition, our Xiamen G5.5 LTPS production line is the first line in China which is capable of producing and selling in full capacity; our Shanghai G5.5 AMOLED production line has been lighten, mass produced and delivered in Mainland China in advanced; our Wuhan G6 LTPS AMOLED production line is in construction phase.


	 


	    We have established manufacturing facilities in Shenzhen, Shanghai, Chengdu, Wuhan, and Xiamen, China as well as in Akita, Japan. In addition, a global sales and technical support network has been put in place that includes offices in the United States, Germany, South Korea, Taiwan, Hong Kong etc. to ensure seamless global support to our customers.


	 


	    With the profound accumulation of technologies, production line development and talent reserve, Tianma will continue to focus on serving display markets worldwide based on technology innovation. With our core values of “Passion, Effectiveness, Win-Win” and our mission “To Create Colorful Life”, Tianma is dedicated to be the world‘s well-respected leading display company.


	 


	 



		Shenzhen Tianma
	














				Shenzhen Tianma covers about 60 thousand square meters, having monochrome LCD production line and high-end car production line, and the products mainly used in automotive, medical, industrial control display and module.
			



		Shanghai Tianma
	














				Shanghai Tianma was founded on April 7, 2006 in the east of Pudong Zhangjiang Hi-tech Industry Park of Shanghai, with registered capital of 1.03 billion yuan RMB and the total investment of 3.29billion yuan RMB, and it covers about 300 thousand square meters. It has a Gen 4.5 TFT-LCD production line, position to Small-to-medium-sized display market, and the products mainly used in automotive, medical, industrial control display and module.
			



		Chengdu Tianma
	






				Chengdu Tianma was founded on September 11, 2008 in the west of Chengdu Hi-tech Development Zone, with registered capital of 1.2 billion yuan RMB and the total investment of 3 billion yuan RMB, and it covers about 300 thousand square meters. It has a Gen 4.5 TFT-LCD production line, position to Small-to-medium-sized display market, and the products mainly used in mobile devices, automotive, industrial control display.
			



		Wuhan Tianma
	














				Wuhan Tianma was founded on November 17,2008 in Optical Valley in China——East Lake Hi-tech Industrial Park of Wuhan, with registered capital of 7.78 billion yuan RMB and the total investment of 16.6 billion yuan RMB, and it covers about 1220 thousand square meters. It has a Gen 4.5 TFT-LCD production line and a CF production line, position to Small-to-medium-sized display market, and the products mainly used in mobile devices, industrial control display and module. At present, a new Gen 6 LTPS AMOLED production line and a CF production line has been lightened in China in advance, of which the products will be used in high-end smart phone and differentiated tablet, etc.
			



		Xiamen Tianma
	














				Xiamen Tianma is a joint venture by AVIC International Holding, AVIC Shenzhen, AVIC Xiamen, and Xiamen JinCai investment Co., LTD. It was founded on March3, 2011 in Xiamen Xiang' an District, with registered capital of 8.8 billion yuan RMB and the total investment of 19 billion yuan RMB, and it covers about 580 thousand square meters. It has a Gen 5.5 LTPS TFT-LCD production line and a CF production line, position to Small-to-medium-sized display market, and the products mainly used in high-end mobile devices display and module. At present, a new Gen 6 LTPS TFT-LCD production line and a CF production line has been mass produced and delivered in Mainland China in advance, of which the products will be used in high-end smart phone and differentiated tablets, etc.
			



		Shanghai AVIC
	














				Shanghai AVIC Optoelectronics was founded on December 11, 2009 in Xinzhuang Industrial Zone of Minhang District, Shanghai, with registered capital of 1.6 billion yuan RMB and the total investment of 2.5 billion yuan RMB, and it covers about 200 thousand square meters. It has a Gen 5 TFT-LCD production line, position to Small-to-medium-sized display market, and the products mainly used in mobile devices, automotive, medical, industrial control display and module.
			



		Tianma Japan, Ltd.
	














				Tianma Japan, Ltd. is a joint venture by AVIC Shenzhen and NEC Corporation, and its predecessor was NEC LCD Technologies, Ltd..The head office is located in Shin-Kawasaki Mitsui Building West Tower 28F 1-1-2, Kashimada, Saiwai-ku, Kawasaki, Kanagawa, Japan. And the plant is located in 3-1-1 Goshono shimotsutsumi, Akita, Akita 010-1412, Japan，covering 130 thousand square meters. It has a Gen 2 and a Gen 3 TFT-LCD production line, and the products mainly used in automotive, medical, industrial control display and module.
			



		Shanghai Tianma AMOLED
	














				Tianma AMOLED is a joint venture by Shanghai Industrial Investment (group) Co., LTD., Shanghai Zhangjiang (group) Co., LTD., and Shanghai Tianma Microelectronics Co., LTD., founded in Pudong district of Shanghai, with registered capital of 1 billion yuan RMB and the total investment of 1.55 billion yuan RMB, and it covers about 120 thousand square meters. It has a Gen 5.5 AMOLED production line, position to Small-to-medium-sized display market, and the products mainly used in mobile devices, etc.
			









                     



